high_descs: Turn right and walk to the recycle bin.
Pick up the tomato from the recycle bin.
Turn around and walk to the door then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Cool the tomato off in the fridge then take it out.
Turn around and walk to the white table.
Place the tomato on the left front side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato on the white table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the green recycle bin on the floor to your right.
Pull the tomato out of the green recycle bin on the floor.
Turn to your right and step into the larger kitchen area, then turn to your right again and go to the refrigerator ahead of you to the left.
Place the tomato on the second shelf, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the tomato from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the white table against the wall.
Place the tomato on the table to the left of the head of lettuce near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the recycling bin on the left.
Pick up the tomato in the bin.
Turn around, bring the tomato to the fridge on the left.
Chill the tomato in the fridge.
Bring the chilled tomato to the table opposite the fridge.
Put the chilled tomato on the table, left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on the table.
